name: Alamosa County Public Health Department
tweet: Update: The Warming Shelter at the Ortega Middle School in Alamosa is only open until 4pm this afternoon. At that time, it will move to the Methodist Church on Mullins Ave. If you are still without power or need a place to warm up, drive safe and come to the shelter if needed.

name: Alamosa County Public Health Department
tweet: A warming shelter has been established at the Ortega Middle School in Alamosa for those who are out of power or who need a place to stay warm! Drive safe and come to the shelter if needed. #StayWarmAlamosa
